{"tid":734701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【假聞散播者名單】會員「胡力威（掙扎中）」散播Fake news 人人得而誅之","createTime":"2018-07-09T01:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T09:37:47.000Z","uid":138409,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4570bb181e86157d4ed0d41d291d81dff8ab75f8","tid":734701,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:13:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">會員編號：</span><br />\n#7699<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">username: </span><br />\n胡力威（掙扎中）、隨機打人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">事件：</span><br />\n於2018-7-8出po指 德國一歲女童遭伊斯蘭移民斬首殺害，而默克爾下令封鎖消息<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/734415/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/734415/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n但係後來有巴打fact check發現係fake news<br />\n而且google搜尋結果<span style=\"color: red;\">第一個</span>已經係正確資訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">圖片證據：</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/090523_0f9a7a7066ca72516227db0c11b93880.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F090523_0f9a7a7066ca72516227db0c11b93880.png&h=5838b34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出po<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/090523_6c3a96fc9893be86447d4cb51de006bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F090523_6c3a96fc9893be86447d4cb51de006bc.png&h=005a2b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打fact check<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/090523_ffd55d105030e4b8fe8a5358a51456fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F090523_ffd55d105030e4b8fe8a5358a51456fb.png&h=e95ed2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請善用google<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/090524_8aa3729e00b56c610d868744232813ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F090524_8aa3729e00b56c610d868744232813ad.png&h=f33b4ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/091323_05b3d8f3aff5b3ba000d3e4dc033be9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F091323_05b3d8f3aff5b3ba000d3e4dc033be9d.jpg&h=3b212e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 'A lie can travel half way around the world while the truth is putting on its shoes.'</span><br />\n</span></span><br />\n&mdash;Mark Twain"},{"pid":"3e4ef4d6a0bc059fa2277f80267801641a94984e","tid":734701,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:15:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"17d1be29b894955e833c4bef60cff5175606bec4","tid":734701,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233cbcbbc6bf702ee8393412ac97c0e4acd05501","tid":734701,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:16:32.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842effb25407333ae1af9c8b3f3b93ed75b81b77","tid":734701,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab51e817f09136b05ab40571873107fcb8280d8d","tid":734701,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,